overview.en: VTM is the general token for the circulation of vitamins in commercial ecology. Total 2.1 billion.VTM is designed with the concept of gamification,and at the same time creates a more vivid, fun, interesting consumption experience with incentive mechanism, And, This is the vision to establish a new token system to empower all communities of interest in the community ecology.
overview.zh: VTM是维他命商业生态内流通的通证。总量21亿。VTM以游戏化通证的理念设计，创造更加生动、好玩、有趣、自带激励机制的消费体验，并以此为愿景建立一个全新通证系统，为社群生态中一切利益共同体赋能。
